source.name: Patent Grant Optical Character Recognition (OCR) Text (1920 - 1979)
source.description: Contains patent grant text produced by an Optical Character Recognition (OCR) process using the U.S. Patent Grant single-page TIFF Image data from January 1920 through December 1979 as input. The file format is modified Patent Full-Text/APS (a.k.a., modified Green Book), ASCII text.
